data.text:
Princess Beatrice of York is the elder daughter of Prince Andrew, Duke of York and Sarah, Duchess of York. She has one sister - Princess Eugenie of York - and is ninth in line to the throne.

In September 2019 she announced her engagement to boyfriend Edoardo Mapelli Mozzi. The couple married in secret in July 2020.

Princess Beatrice is currently pregnant with the couple's first child.
